{"id":8413,"name":null,"username":"ChaosFish","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/chaosfish/{size}/2_2.png","created_at":"2005-04-30T21:32:23.000Z","cooked":"<p>Yep its true!! Really!<br>\nCheck my sig or go <a href=\"http://lba.fishos.cc/hebrew/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a>!</p>\n<p>Have fun playing LBA2 in Hebrew!!</p>\n<p>Id like to give a million thanks to Zink and to OBrasilo. Without their AMAZINGLY good willing and hard working help, this translation would probably never excisted.</p>\n<p>KIFAK HEY to Obras!</p>\n<p>KIFAK HEY to Zink!</p>\n<p>I am very happy now. Yes. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>The translators are morshem and myself.</p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":16,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T15:22:48.124Z","reply_count":10,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":7,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":85.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":8410,"topic_slug":"lba2-is-now-in-full-hebrew","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Yep it's true!! Really!\nCheck my sig or go [here](http://lba.fishos.cc/hebrew/)!\n\nHave fun playing LBA2 in Hebrew!!\n\nI'd like to give a million thanks to Zink and to OBrasilo. Without their AMAZINGLY good willing and hard working help, this translation would probably never excisted.\n\nKIFAK HEY to Obras!\n\nKIFAK HEY to Zink!\n\nI am very happy now. Yes. :)\n\nThe translators are morshem and myself.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"group_moderator":true,"user_id":2,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-is-now-in-full-hebrew/8410/1","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null,"can_vote":false}
